data_case_d_metal
#
# Case D (the frontier): one Ca at a two-chain interface, coordinated by acidic residues from
# chains A and B, each modelled in alternates. sphere_a / sphere_b are the coordination networks;
# they share the coexistence group "coord_sphere" and additionally carry an explicit NOT row.
# _struct_conn carries the alternate-specific metalc bonds. (Spheres C/D omitted for brevity.)
#
